      You guessed it – we’re diligently working on a new Outlook Calendar
      integration that’ll bring the joy of time-blocking to all you Outlook
      enthusiasts. We’ll also be exploring ways to display completed tasks
      within the calendar layout in Todoist, so you can easily track your
      achievements over time.<br />
      <br />
      In the meantime, <a href="https://doist.typeform.com/to/utRsZMxc?utm_source=todoist&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=2024_10_todoist_monthly">let us know what you think of the new Sync tasks feature</a>. We’d love to hear from you as we continue to refine the calendar
      experience in Todoist.<br />
      <br />
